      "rationale": "Testing conducted at a single quasi-static displacement rate (5 mm/min) per ASTM F1717. No variation in temperature, humidity, or loading rate explored. This limits generalizability but is consistent with the standard protocol. Test conditions level 1 achieved — below required level 2; gap accepted given standard compliance and medium model influence."
