      "rationale": "Displacement boundary conditions replicated ASTM F1717 fixture geometry. Applied displacement ramp matched experimental crosshead displacement. Set-screw preload torque applied in FEA via equivalent bolt pretension element. Equivalency confirmed by sensitivity analysis showing <2% QoI change over ±10% preload variation. Equivalency level 2 achieved."
